Sales Manager
Galadari Group
Date: 01-05-2014
Job Type: Contract
Job Status: Full Time
Categories:
Manufacturing & Production
Managerial
Galadari Group
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
To achieve the budgeted profits and revenue independently and through the sales team. Respond efficiently to enquiries with appropriate information about company's products and services and competitors. Maintain up-to-date information/data of all customers. Participates in the company’s marketing efforts in trade shows & conference. Ensure effective account management of existing clientele. Motivates and drive the sales team towards the goal. Ensures department’s compliance to International Organization of Standardization, Company’s code of Conduct, and Department’s Standard Operating procedure. Areas – GCC Regions and  UAE. email:vacancies@gits.ae
Requirements
Minimum 8-10 years’ experience in similar business activities and in sales & Marketing Operations.Skills: Estimation / Calculation, Profound knowledge on auto-corrosive linings, material handling systems, Marine fender systems, etc.
